== Spanish ==

==== Etymology ====
Latin ''[[quam]]''

==== Adverb ====

'''cuan'''

# [[how]], to what [[extent]].

==== Usage notes ====

Used with adjectives.  Rare in modern speech, usually replaced with [[que]], [[tan]], or [[cuanto]].  Written with an accent mark (''cuán'') when exclamative, as in ''¡cuán grande es!''

